description: NSLOCTEXT("", "803F43F94F86A3DB39FBE1B535CA3C3B", "The Highwaymen leader, Orrik Blackwood, has hired me and a burglar named Splint to infiltrate the ruins he once called refuge. A band of minotaurs has seized control and now the bandit king hopes to drive them out by unleashing an ancient curse upon them.
